tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE social_media_data (
    post_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    post_date TIMESTAMP,
    post_content TEXT,
    influencer_id UUID,
    likes INT,
    comments INT
);

CREATE TABLE Collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    brand_name VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);
CREATE TABLE influencers (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), followers INT, engagement_rate DECIMAL(5,2));
CREATE TABLE posts (id INT PRIMARY KEY, influencer_id INT, content TEXT, post_date DATE);
CREATE TABLE collaborations (id INT PRIMARY KEY, post_id INT, collaborator VARCHAR(50), collaboration_type VARCHAR(50));

CREATE TABLE Collaborations (
    collaboration_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT NOT NULL,
    brand_id INT NOT NULL,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    collaboration_date DATE NOT NULL,
    collaboration_budget DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Posts (
    post_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT NOT NULL,
    post_content TEXT NOT NULL,
    post_likes INT NOT NULL,
    post_comments INT NOT NULL,
    post_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    brand_id INT,
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
    collaboration_date DATE
);
